                    "body": "Note that if you use DOS-style <code>CMD.EXE</code>, you don&#39;t have a fancy shell that expands <code>*</code> for you, so this passes the literal <code>*</code> to Git. The result is slightly different than if you are using bash or some other Unix-like shell that <i>does</i> expand <code>*</code> for you."
