                            "body": "Since you both answered my question I had trouble deciding who to give credit to. I chose Denis below because he has less rep than you. So I figured giving him the green check would benefit him more than it would benefit you. I hope that makes sense? But I really appreciate both explanations. Thanks!"
                        },
