                            "link": "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/26042390/git-add-asterisk-vs-git-add-period/26042516#comment131618541_26042516",
                            "body": "for completeness, if you quote <code>*</code> it won&#39;t be expanded by the shell, but git will still interpret it and stage all files in current directory, including dot and deleted files."
